snippet.title: Super Mario Odyssey: Kaizo Mode - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Over a year in the making, the first full 880 moon mod for SMO has been made by me and SMOJoycon.

Music used in trailer:
https://youtu.be/h5BA0m2F29E?si=3Fw_5PRIvX0CcQTK
https://youtu.be/MTxMh6qu6Mw?si=uOWgYNG-PMyAY2jL


          Special thanks:

Chico (and the whole modding server) - Fixing so many issues we would never have been able to
Skellux - Huge inspiration from Superstar Mode

Crazalu - Logo
Kale, Lex, Zack207, Gamenerd, Gamesjam, Jimmy - Hint arts

SMOjoycon - Working on the mod with me for the last year

Download: gamebanana.com/mods/529956
